descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone, here is my Breton/Elf looking character Preset ..I've based this character on the Sephinroth from Might and Magic Heroes VII, she's a sort of evil trickster who uses a lot of dark magic and stuff so she would probably be better as an evil character but that's entirely up to you. There's a few mods I used during the process of making this character so if you like the looks of it so far then the mods I've used are listed below.
[color=#00ff00]There's now a new and improved Version 2 of this character preset![/color]

Requirements:

Racemenu   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624[/url]﻿

SG eyebrows   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327[/url]﻿

KS Hairdos - HDT Physics   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363[/url]﻿

Vampire eyes playable   [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26222]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26222[/url]


Thank you to all of the fantastic modders for supplying the, you know.. mods, credit goes to:

Racemenu - expired6978
SG eyebrows - hellosanta
KS Hairdos - HDT Physics - Stealthic Khaos
Vampire eyes playable - dark1402



Here's a bit of information about Sephinroth's character from MMH7:

[i]"Born Saifiros, "sharp steel eyes", this master con artist changed her name to "Sephinroth" because she felt it sounded more exotic and regal, giving her an aura of mystery. A skillful liar, she tried to pass herself as the late King Arniel's illegitimate daughter. When the masquerade was discovered, Sephinroth was forced to hide among the exiled Dark Elves."[/i]
author: ratman186
